msgid "Um... okay..."
msgstr "嗯...好吧..."

msgid "A realistic sculpture of a man with a candle for a head."
msgstr "一尊有着蜡烛头的逼真人物雕塑。"

msgid "(What should I do?)"
msgstr "（我该做什么？）"

msgid "Touch it"
msgstr "触碰它"

msgid "Take the candle"
msgstr "拿走蜡烛"

msgid "Blow out the candle"
msgstr "吹灭蜡烛"

msgid "Do nothing"
msgstr "什么也不做"

msgid "The statue feels like stone, just as you would expect."
msgstr "雕像摸起来就像石头，跟你预期的一样。"

msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr "你确定吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Artist_3F.misc_candleman.choice.Are you sure?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Artist_3F.misc_candleman.choice.Are you sure?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Leftovers of what was once a sculpture."
msgstr "残骸，曾是雕塑。"

msgid "The candle man is gone."
msgstr "蜡烛人走了。"

msgid "It's hard to tell what it says from this side."
msgstr "从这边很难看清楚上面写的是什么。"

msgid "It reads: \"Exhibit closed indefinitely. If you have complaints, please direct them back to where they came from.\""
msgstr "上面写道：\"画廊无限期关闭。 如果您有任何投诉意见，请将其捎给意见本人。\""

msgid "The sculpture is either broken or unfinished. You can't really tell."
msgstr "这尊雕像要么是坏了，要么是没完成。你说不准。"

msgid "A tall vase."
msgstr "一个高大的花瓶。"

msgid "Reach inside?"
msgstr "要伸手进去吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Artist_3F.misc_vase.choice.Reach inside?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Artist_3F.misc_vase.choice.Reach inside?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "...tired..."
msgstr "...累..."

msgid "...so....tired...."
msgstr "...好...累..."
